  "body": "The eth.miner() object in mist only has the option stop() and start(), with no way currently to set how much mining your machine should do. In practice it means that it's currently only capable of two states: \"off\" and \"turn all your computer fans to desperate mode\".\n\nThe mining/network dashboard already supports a sliding scale in the interface, I only need a way to do that in go.\n",
